    body#page-top


        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.fixed-top
            .container
                a.navbar-brand(href='./')
                    img(src='assets/img/ogc-logo-white.svg', alt='...')

        section#adopters.page-section
            .container
                .text-left
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase blogs
                    p.text-muted 
                        | Blogs run by thought leaders and geospatial experts from the community, which may ocasionaly talk about #OGCAPI, among other (geospatial) things.
